snippet.title: Trolls vs Vikings: Reborn - First Trailer
snippet.description:
The original Tower Defense fun of Trolls vs Vikings is back with a revamped and upgraded experience that enthralled over 1.3 million players around the world in the past 10 years. 

First Demo available during Steam's Real-Time Strategy Festival.
Check it now at: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2940040/Trolls_vs_Vikings_Reborn

For more information:
Discord: https://discord.gg/P4aTmj8 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TrollsVsVikings
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/megapopgames/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/MegapopGames
